## Completeness Checklist
- [ ] Story-level DoD agreed by team
- [ ] Sprint-level DoD agreed by team
- [ ] Phase-level DoD agreed by team and Product Owner
- [ ] AI/ML additions included where product involves AI/ML
- [ ] Exception log maintained for any waivers
